text: Autingues is a commune in the Pas-de-Calais department in northern France. ==Geography== A village located 10 miles (16 km) southeast of Calais, at the junction of the D225 with the D227 road. ==Population== ==Sights== * The eighteenth-century church of St. Louis. * The eighteenth-century château. ==See also== *Communes of the Pas-de-Calais department ==References== * INSEE commune file Category:Communes of Pas-de-Calais
title: Autingues
